@startuml sequence

skinparam monochrome false
skinparam backgroundColor #191A1C
skinparam defaultFontName "Malgun Gothic"
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

skinparam defaultFontColor #E0E0E0
skinparam arrowColor #7EC8E3
skinparam arrowFontColor #E0E0E0

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #2E3033
    BorderColor #666666
    FontColor #E0E0E0
}

skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #2E3033
    BorderColor #666666
    FontColor #E0E0E0
}

skinparam sequence {
    LifeLineBorderColor #555555
    GroupBackgroundColor #252628
    GroupBorderColor #555555
    GroupFontColor #E0E0E0
    GroupHeaderFontColor #7EC8E3
    DividerBackgroundColor #252628
    DividerBorderColor #555555
    DividerFontColor #E0E0E0
    ReferenceBackgroundColor #252628
    ReferenceBorderColor #555555
}

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #2E3033
    BorderColor #666666
    FontColor #E0E0E0
}

skinparam title {
    FontColor #E0E0E0
}

title 돌의 정령 챗봇 - 시퀀스 다이어그램

actor User
participant "Unity / Gradio" as Client
participant "FastAPI\nserver.py" as Server
participant "NPC_manager.py" as NPC
participant "ChromaDB" as DB
participant "GPT-5.4-mini" as GPT
participant "Pydantic\nValidator" as Val

User -> Client : 메시지 입력
Client -> Client : 플레이어 말풍선 표시\n(입력 텍스트 즉시 반영)
Client -> Server : POST /chat\n{message, session_id}
Server -> NPC : chat(message)

NPC -> DB : query(message, n=2)
DB --> NPC : 관련 문서 반환

NPC -> GPT : system_prompt + context + history
GPT --> NPC : 응답 텍스트

loop 최대 3회 재시도
    NPC -> Val : SpiritResponse(text)
    alt 검증 통과
        Val --> NPC : validated
    else 검증 실패\n(금지어미 / 영어 / 빈 응답)
        Val --> NPC : ValidationError
        NPC -> GPT : 재요청
        GPT --> NPC : 응답 텍스트
    end
end

NPC --> Server : reply + token usage
Server --> Client : ChatResponse JSON
Client --> Client : NPC 말풍선 표시\n(자동 크기 조절)
Client --> User : 화면 출력

@enduml
